This paper deals with quantum error correction codes and circuits, which are primarily studied in the quantum computing (cs.QU) sub-category. The paper also involves algorithms for manipulating and computing properties of stabilizer states, which can be seen as a problem in data structures (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also involves the study of stabilizer frames, which can be seen as a problem in coding theory (cs.CC) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
